wikitext.*:
{{year-header}}

==January==
* '''[[3 January|3]]''' - [[Birthday Toast#Tolkien Society tradition|Birthday Toast]].

==March==
* '''[[25 March|25]]''' - [[Tolkien Reading Day]].
* '''[[30 March|30]]''' - ''[[The Battle of Maldon: together with The Homecoming of Beorhtnoth]]'' is published in the UK.

==April==
* '''[[22 April|22]]''' - Australian actor [[Barry Humphries]] dies.

==May==
* '''[[10 May|10]]''' - ''[[The Lord of the Rings: Heroes of Middle-earth]]'' is released online.
* '''[[25 May|25]]''' - ''[[The Lord of the Rings: Gollum]]'' is released.

==June==
* '''[[6 June|6]]''' - ''[[The Battle of Maldon: together with The Homecoming of Beorhtnoth]]'' is published in the US.
* '''[[21 June|21]]''' - Filming for the second season of ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Rings of Power]]'' is wrapped.

==July==
* '''[[2 July|2]]''' - The 2023 [[Tolkien Society]] seminar, takes place at The Hilton Leeds City and it is held Online.
* '''[[25 July|25]]''' - [[The Lord of the Rings (musical)]] opens at the Watermill Theatre in [[Wikipedia:Newbury, Berkshire|Newbury]], West Berkshire. 

==August==
* '''[[15 August|15]]''' - ''[[Tolkien Calendar 2024]]'' is published.
* '''[[18 August|18]]''' - Game developer [[Wendell Lariston Hill, Jr.]] dies.
* '''[[31 August|31]] - [[3 September]]''' - [[Oxonmoot 2023]] is held.
*

==September==
* '''[[2 September|2]]''' - ''[[Tolkien's Faith]]'' is published.
* '''[[9 September|9]]''' - Actor [[Peter McKenzie]] dies.

==October==
* '''[[15 October|15]]''' - [[The Lord of the Rings (musical)]] ends at the Watermill Theatre in [[Wikipedia:Newbury, Berkshire|Newbury]], West Berkshire. 
* '''[[24 October|24]]''' - ''[[The Lord of the Rings: Return to Moria]]'' is released on PC.

==November==
* '''[[8 November|8]]''' - ''[[The Lord of the Rings Online: Corsairs of Umbar]]'' is released online.
* '''[[9 November|9]] - A revised and expanded edition of ''[[The Letters of J.R.R. Tolkien]]'' is published in the UK.'''

==December==
* '''[[7 December|7]]''' - [[Christopher Tolkien Centenary Boxed Sets]] #1 is released
